<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4243.1.2>
    dc:creator "González-Durán, Gustavo A.; Targino, Mariane; Rada, Marco; Grant, Taran" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Phylogenetic relationships and morphology of the Pristimantis leptolophus species group (Amphibia: Anura: Brachycephaloidea), with the recognition of a new species group in Pristimantis Jiménez de la Espada, 1870" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.398701> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.398701>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Second part of the consensus tree showing the phylogenetic relationships of Brachycephaloidea (Pristimantis myersi, P. leptolophus, P. boulengeri, P. devillei species group and unassigned species) as recovered by the 108 most parsimonious trees obtained with direct optimization (length 24341 steps) under equal weights for all transformations. Institutional collection codes follow Sabaj-Pérez (2014). Photos by Marco Rada, John Lynch and Giovany Chaves. Values above nodes are Goodman-Bremer support." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/398701/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

